<p><strong>Security Clearance:</strong> Qliphoth</p>
<p><strong>Duties:</strong> The Administrator is more of an editor than a writer. Over many years, he has seen the rise and fall of countless SCP documents. If found, please contact Overwatch Command for pickup.</p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-left" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/expanded-biography-of-the-administrator/admin02.jpg" style="width:200px;" alt="admin02.jpg" class="image" />
