<p><sub><em>Eventually, when I really buckled down to start looking for stuff, I found that most of what I'd lost wasn't really that lost. I knew where it was, per se, but I couldn't find it. But it wasn't lost. It was just misplaced. I was still in control, and I could, and I can, still find everything if I looked hard enough.</em></sub></p>
<p><em><sub>It'll all turn up eventually. Don't panic.</sub></em></p>
<h1 id="toc9"><span>PERSONNEL REPORTS</span></h1>
